/**
 * Q-075 mutation-hardening GOLDEN tests (2026-07-16).
 *
 * The 2026-07-12 Stryker run scored lib/backtest at 31.22 — the existing
 * suites assert structure and bounds, which arithmetic/conditional mutants
 * sail through. These tests pin EXACT numeric outputs of the engines on
 * deterministic synthetic fixtures, so any mutation of the accounting,
 * annualization, cost, windowing, or scoring math shifts a pinned value.
 *
 * The pinned values are CHARACTERIZATION goldens generated by running these
 * exact fixtures through the shipped implementation. If an INTENDED behavior
 * change moves them, update the pins from the failure diff in the same
 * commit — a silent drift is exactly what these tests exist to catch.
 *
 * Feature flag: the engine goldens run with QUANTAN_USE_ENHANCED_SIGNAL=0
 * (the PRODUCTION signal path — regime-only); enhanced-path pins stub it on.
 */
